Introduction

Wang Ke is a Chinese singer. She is a member of the girl group Gen1es, the Chinese girl group AIM, and a former member of the pre-debut Korean girl group HOWZ.

She is known for being a contestant on the South Korean reality survival show, Produce 48, where she was eliminated in episode 8 after ranking 56th.

In 2024, she competed in the reality survival show, Chuang Asia Thailand, where she ranked 6th overall, thus becoming a member of the girl group Gen1es.
